title: England Women crash out of the T20 World Cup
description: Henry Moeran is joined by Tash Farrant, Katherine Sciver-Brunt and Daniel Norcross in Dubai, bringing reaction to England Women crashing out of the tournament, after West Indies beat them by 6 wickets. We’ll hear from both captains, Heather Knight and Hayley Matthews.
author: BBC Radio 5 Live
